WEBVTT

01:00.880 --> 01:01.400
Xu Xiao.

01:05.360 --> 01:05.800
How did it go?

01:05.800 --> 01:06.400
Got it.

01:33.920 --> 01:35.050
Are we almost there?

01:36.039 --> 01:36.770
Right ahead.

01:37.520 --> 01:38.120
Okay.

01:52.840 --> 01:53.370
Let's go.

02:01.680 --> 02:02.340
Brother Hu.

02:08.479 --> 02:09.139
Brother Hu.

02:22.600 --> 02:23.240
Xu Xiao,

02:24.280 --> 02:25.810
what are you burning today?

02:35.160 --> 02:35.600
Okay.

02:36.480 --> 02:38.000
I'll squeeze you in.

02:43.120 --> 02:44.120
This is a gas kiln.

02:44.320 --> 02:45.320
It's usually for home use.

02:45.320 --> 02:46.000
Large porcelain factories

02:46.000 --> 02:48.329
usually won't fire a single piece for you.

02:51.720 --> 02:54.320
Brother Hu started working at such a young age.

02:54.360 --> 02:56.040
It's their own family business.

02:56.040 --> 02:57.480
In this kind of family workshop,

02:57.480 --> 02:58.960
many kids follow their parents

02:58.960 --> 03:00.240
to work together from a young age.

03:00.240 --> 03:03.440
Their skills aren't necessarily worse than those from the ceramics department in schools.

03:03.440 --> 03:04.970
As expected of Jingdezhen,

03:05.200 --> 03:08.000
a place where even three-year-olds play with mud.

03:20.880 --> 03:21.720
Fatty, let go.

03:24.440 --> 03:25.300
Is that polite?

03:25.800 --> 03:26.660
Is that polite?

03:27.800 --> 03:28.280
Sir.

03:29.840 --> 03:30.440
Xiaocen.

03:31.240 --> 03:32.040
Are you okay?

03:32.920 --> 03:34.560
Mr. Fatty is so spoiled.

03:35.200 --> 03:37.120
He's always trying to get my attention.

03:37.120 --> 03:38.360
Every now and then, from my desk,

03:38.360 --> 03:40.560
he grabs something shiny.

03:41.560 --> 03:43.620
Look, he took my Nanhong Agate again.

03:43.680 --> 03:45.810
His place has become a treasure trove.

03:46.440 --> 03:47.440
Come, sit.

03:47.800 --> 03:48.200
Okay.

03:48.720 --> 03:51.380
This is freshly arrived Mingqian Longjing tea.

03:52.520 --> 03:53.250
Let's try it.

03:54.960 --> 03:55.640
Sir,

03:56.440 --> 03:57.520
what is this?

03:59.079 --> 04:00.320
Isn't this the one at our entrance,

04:00.320 --> 04:01.360
the best-selling

04:01.360 --> 04:03.820
small cup with the Hundred Family Surnames?

04:03.960 --> 04:05.890
The unglazed body looks like this.

04:07.240 --> 04:08.170
Meeting is fate.

04:08.200 --> 04:09.200
I'll give you one.

04:09.240 --> 04:09.770
This one,

04:10.600 --> 04:11.360
this one is not bad.

04:11.360 --> 04:12.560
The shape is regular.

04:13.760 --> 04:14.290
Tonight,

04:14.800 --> 04:17.079
I will find someone to write the character Cen on it.

04:17.079 --> 04:17.920
Tomorrow, it goes into the kiln,

04:17.920 --> 04:20.560
and I'll deliver it to your house the day after tomorrow.

04:20.560 --> 04:21.160
Sir.

04:22.200 --> 04:23.080
Can I

04:23.760 --> 04:25.420
write this character myself?

04:25.440 --> 04:26.500
Write it yourself?

04:39.640 --> 04:40.080
Sir,

04:40.600 --> 04:41.530
I've written it.

04:41.720 --> 04:42.320
Let me see.

04:47.280 --> 04:48.760
Your handwriting is quite good.

04:48.760 --> 04:49.880
This Slender Gold Script

04:49.880 --> 04:51.280
has some real character.

04:52.600 --> 04:53.840
Xiaocen, your writing is great.

04:53.840 --> 04:54.320
For writing like this,

04:54.320 --> 04:55.440
if I hired someone outside to do it,

04:55.440 --> 04:56.500
it would cost a lot.

05:00.120 --> 05:00.800
Xiaocen.

05:02.120 --> 05:02.560
You know what?

05:02.560 --> 05:04.320
I really envy you young folks.

05:05.080 --> 05:05.940
Do you know why?

05:07.800 --> 05:09.800
Because you have plenty of time.

05:10.200 --> 05:11.400
Time is money.

05:12.000 --> 05:12.860
Look at Xu Xiao.

05:13.240 --> 05:15.480
He spends a lot of his time here,

05:15.880 --> 05:17.440
turning time that would be meaningless

05:17.440 --> 05:19.040
into something meaningful.

05:22.440 --> 05:24.570
Are you interested in a part-time job?

05:25.640 --> 05:26.570
A part-time job?

05:26.720 --> 05:27.440
For one cup,

05:27.720 --> 05:29.050
I'll give you five yuan.

05:29.560 --> 05:31.320
Don't look down on this five yuan.

05:31.320 --> 05:33.520
We can produce a dozen pieces a day here.

05:33.880 --> 05:35.010
That's 60 or 70 yuan.

05:35.120 --> 05:35.880
Added up over a month,

05:35.880 --> 05:37.159
think about how much that is.

05:37.159 --> 05:37.640
Right?

05:38.320 --> 05:39.200
Most importantly,

05:39.200 --> 05:40.659
the money doesn't matter.

05:41.320 --> 05:43.440
Xu works here every day,

05:43.440 --> 05:44.900
and he gets pretty lonely.

05:45.240 --> 05:47.040
You two can keep each other company.

05:47.040 --> 05:48.770
You two are classmates, right?

05:50.120 --> 05:51.440
What are you guys talking about?

05:51.440 --> 05:52.000
Xu,

05:52.240 --> 05:53.370
you're just in time.

05:53.480 --> 05:55.600
Xiaocen is going to work here.

05:56.320 --> 05:58.120
Come on, meet your new coworker.

06:02.920 --> 06:03.960
I never thought

06:04.280 --> 06:06.560
I could ever be of use.

06:07.520 --> 06:09.450
Someone actually wants to hire me.

06:09.880 --> 06:12.000
You don't need to sell yourself short.

06:12.000 --> 06:13.060
You are excellent.

06:16.920 --> 06:18.280
Actually,

06:19.680 --> 06:22.000
I've always felt quite ordinary.

06:23.000 --> 06:23.960
Just like

06:24.920 --> 06:26.720
a little pile of dirt by the road.

06:27.640 --> 06:29.370
You think you're a pile of dirt,

06:29.720 --> 06:30.520
but actually,

06:31.120 --> 06:32.850
you are unrefined kaolin clay.

06:33.440 --> 06:34.200
Kaolin Clay.

06:34.680 --> 06:35.080
Right.

06:35.960 --> 06:37.360
Isn't it still just clay?

06:37.640 --> 06:38.159
No.

06:38.360 --> 06:40.200
It's the most suitable clay

06:45.640 --> 06:46.600
for making ceramics.

06:46.600 --> 06:47.060
Sister.

06:48.159 --> 06:48.880
Xing, it's your turn.

06:48.880 --> 06:49.480
Hurry.

06:51.640 --> 06:52.700
What are you doing?

06:52.840 --> 06:53.280
Go.

06:53.960 --> 06:54.760
What's wrong?

06:58.880 --> 06:59.720
This is my classmate.

06:59.720 --> 07:00.480
This is my brother-in-law.

07:00.480 --> 07:01.740
What brother-in-law?

07:01.840 --> 07:02.560
This is...

07:02.560 --> 07:03.620
I'm her classmate.

07:03.680 --> 07:04.680
My name is Xu Xiao.

07:04.800 --> 07:05.640
It's too late today,

07:05.640 --> 07:06.800
so I brought her back.

07:06.800 --> 07:08.480
Then you're the future brother-in-law.

07:08.480 --> 07:09.880
Brother-in-Law, run quickly.

07:09.880 --> 07:11.680
My Aunt must be watching from upstairs.

07:11.680 --> 07:12.960
It'll be trouble if she sees you.

07:12.960 --> 07:14.440
Xing can take me back.

07:15.080 --> 07:15.960
You should leave.

07:15.960 --> 07:16.960
Good night, good night.

07:16.960 --> 07:17.520
Let's go.

07:17.760 --> 07:18.280
Brother-in-law.

07:18.280 --> 07:18.960
Good night.

07:19.040 --> 07:21.100
What are you talking about? Hurry up.

07:28.520 --> 07:29.050
Xiaocen.

07:29.720 --> 07:30.250
Xiaocen.

07:31.040 --> 07:31.520
Hello.

07:32.159 --> 07:33.400
What are you guys going to do?

07:33.400 --> 07:34.880
We... we're going fishing.

07:34.880 --> 07:35.320
Yes.

07:35.720 --> 07:36.320
Fishing.

07:36.960 --> 07:38.600
Doesn't the school forbid fishing?

07:38.600 --> 07:41.200
It's fine. Just hide from the security guards.

07:43.159 --> 07:43.680
Bye.

07:43.680 --> 07:44.159
Bye. We're leaving.

07:44.159 --> 07:44.640
Bye.

07:57.760 --> 07:58.490
You're here.

08:00.640 --> 08:01.760
Why are you here?

08:03.680 --> 08:05.940
The four of them swim over occasionally.

08:06.200 --> 08:07.460
I'm going to feed them.

08:08.680 --> 08:09.340
Have a seat.

08:30.640 --> 08:31.700
You really like it.

08:37.640 --> 08:39.169
This is the first porcelain

08:40.039 --> 08:41.640
I've fired in my life.

08:43.400 --> 08:43.880
No,

08:44.920 --> 08:45.920
it's ours.

08:51.200 --> 08:52.320
If you like it,

08:54.400 --> 08:55.460
I'll give it to you.

08:56.280 --> 08:56.840
Really?

09:02.720 --> 09:03.320
Thank you.

09:04.160 --> 09:04.820
No problem.

09:07.400 --> 09:08.840
You two, stop right there.

09:08.840 --> 09:10.080
Bro, we're sorry.

09:10.080 --> 09:10.480
Stop!

09:10.480 --> 09:12.240
Li Zhuoting, hurry up!

09:12.600 --> 09:14.640
Wang Lin, why are you calling my name?

09:14.640 --> 09:15.040
Stop!

09:22.360 --> 09:23.840
Why are you eating popsicles without me?

09:23.840 --> 09:25.300
Who knew if you wanted one?

09:25.440 --> 09:26.720
When mentioning the Tang Dynasty,

09:26.720 --> 09:29.480
most people think of Tang Tri-colored Glazed Pottery.

09:29.480 --> 09:32.320
Like the well-known Tang Tri-colored Pottery Horse.

09:32.320 --> 09:32.920
However,

09:33.680 --> 09:35.160
Tang Tri-colored Glazed Pottery

09:35.160 --> 09:37.480
was not recorded in history.

09:38.560 --> 09:39.640
Initially,

09:40.080 --> 09:42.320
there were no physical objects handed down.

09:42.320 --> 09:43.160
Until when?

09:43.640 --> 09:45.700
It wasn't until the late Qing Dynasty

09:46.000 --> 09:47.920
that in the tombs of the Tang Dynasty,

09:47.920 --> 09:49.760
this porcelain was discovered.

09:50.720 --> 09:51.400
So,

09:52.240 --> 09:55.700
Wang Lin says we're playing a murder mystery game after class.

09:55.880 --> 09:57.440
Ask Wu Jing if she wants to go.

09:57.440 --> 09:58.120
Later,

09:58.520 --> 10:01.600
with the continuous efforts

10:01.680 --> 10:03.360
and excavations by archaeologists,

10:03.360 --> 10:03.820
Wu Jing.

10:04.880 --> 10:05.480
Wu Jing.

10:05.840 --> 10:08.640
Tang Tri-colored Glazed Pottery was discovered.

10:08.880 --> 10:09.540
From where?

10:10.800 --> 10:13.560
From ordinary dwellings to temple ruins.

10:14.000 --> 10:15.680
That's when people gradually learned about

10:15.680 --> 10:17.480
Tang Tri‑colored Glazed Pottery.

10:17.480 --> 10:19.360
Wang Lin, Li Zhuoting.

10:20.240 --> 10:22.360
Are you two in a culture class

10:22.440 --> 10:23.680
or a dance class?

10:24.880 --> 10:26.480
Tang Tri‑colored Glazed Pottery is actually a type of

10:26.480 --> 10:28.000
colorful pottery.

10:28.760 --> 10:29.680
Class is over.

10:30.880 --> 10:32.600
Yuexin, are you going?

10:33.600 --> 10:34.120
Yan Xue.

10:35.360 --> 10:36.000
I'll go if you go.

10:36.000 --> 10:36.600
Let's go.

10:36.680 --> 10:37.960
We don't have class this afternoon anyway.

10:37.960 --> 10:38.690
That's true.

10:38.920 --> 10:39.480
Xiaoyi.

10:40.000 --> 10:41.160
Want to play a murder mystery game?

10:41.160 --> 10:41.680
Sure.

10:43.680 --> 10:44.240
Xiaocen.

10:44.520 --> 10:46.120
We are going to play a murder mystery game this afternoon.

10:46.120 --> 10:47.050
Do you want to go?

10:48.000 --> 10:50.360
I've never played a murder mystery game before.

10:50.360 --> 10:51.160
You don't need to know how.

10:51.160 --> 10:52.440
The DM will guide us through the process.

10:52.440 --> 10:53.300
Just follow me.

10:54.160 --> 10:56.040
DM?

10:56.080 --> 10:56.760
Come on.

10:56.760 --> 10:58.720
You didn't join us for karaoke last time.

10:58.720 --> 10:59.780
Let's go together.

11:02.520 --> 11:03.160
Bye.

11:03.160 --> 11:03.720
Bye.

11:03.920 --> 11:04.880
I like eating that too.

11:04.880 --> 11:05.560
It's my favorite,

11:05.560 --> 11:06.160
and Lonely God too.

11:06.160 --> 11:07.400
I want five bags.

11:07.680 --> 11:08.080
Okay.

11:08.480 --> 11:09.280
You promised.

11:17.320 --> 11:19.250
Let's introduce ourselves first.

11:19.800 --> 11:21.800
I am Imperial Guard Mo Sanfeng.

11:22.000 --> 11:24.480
Hello, everyone. I am Su Yinger.

11:27.120 --> 11:29.760
Hello, everyone. I am Cuiwen, a maid in the prince's mansion.

11:29.760 --> 11:32.090
Hello, everyone. I am Princess Xiangyue.

11:32.600 --> 11:35.120
Hello, everyone. I am Chen, the butler of the prince's mansion.

11:35.120 --> 11:38.200
I am Liu Rushuang, a famous courtesan in the capital.

11:38.200 --> 11:39.930
This role suits you perfectly.

11:40.160 --> 11:43.480
Hello, everyone. I am Eunuch Lin, the head eunuch.

11:59.000 --> 11:59.860
It's your turn.

12:01.000 --> 12:04.040
I am... I am Eunuch Lin.

12:04.800 --> 12:07.880
I was at the prince's mansion that day.

12:09.760 --> 12:11.160
Tell us more information.

12:11.160 --> 12:12.440
What were you doing at the prince's mansion?

12:12.440 --> 12:13.080
Tell us a bit more.

12:13.080 --> 12:13.680
Exactly.

12:13.680 --> 12:14.880
Do you have any clues?

12:18.000 --> 12:20.520
When I was young, I lived in the desert.

12:20.800 --> 12:23.600
I passed by Liu Rushuang's room.

12:23.720 --> 12:24.320
What is she saying?

12:24.320 --> 12:28.040
Although Shazhou was a prosperous place in the Tang Dynasty,

12:28.040 --> 12:29.480
it suffered from years of famine.

12:29.480 --> 12:30.880
Xiaocen. Xiaocen.

12:31.320 --> 12:32.560
Just summarize it yourself

12:32.560 --> 12:33.620
and say it out loud.

12:35.360 --> 12:37.020
I might not summarize it well.

12:38.440 --> 12:39.840
Well, roughly,

12:40.360 --> 12:42.680
I didn't do much at the prince's mansion.

13:22.280 --> 13:23.680
When I was young, I was in the desert.

13:23.680 --> 13:24.880
What is she saying?

13:25.320 --> 13:25.720
I don't know either.

13:25.720 --> 13:28.680
I passed by Liu Rushuang's room.

13:55.800 --> 13:56.920
I feel a little addicted.

13:56.920 --> 13:57.980
It's just us today.

13:58.080 --> 13:59.400
Didn't you call Xiaocen?

13:59.400 --> 14:00.360
She doesn't know how to play.

14:00.360 --> 14:01.480
Let's choose a horror one today.

14:01.480 --> 14:01.840
How about it?

14:01.840 --> 14:02.200
Okay.

14:02.600 --> 14:02.960
Fine.

14:18.640 --> 14:20.040
Do you think this is okay?

14:21.560 --> 14:22.240
Almost.

14:22.480 --> 14:23.240
Put it aside.

14:23.440 --> 14:24.370
I'll do the rest.

14:33.960 --> 14:35.420
Why don't you take a break?

15:45.320 --> 15:46.120
You're awake.

15:46.360 --> 15:47.800
How long was I asleep?

15:49.000 --> 15:49.760
Not for long.

15:55.040 --> 15:56.160
It's already 5:00.

15:58.200 --> 15:58.800
I'm sorry.

15:59.440 --> 16:01.440
I didn't know if I should wake you up.

16:02.240 --> 16:02.880
It's fine.

16:03.400 --> 16:04.880
I rarely sleep so soundly.

18:20.480 --> 18:21.680
I told him,

18:23.200 --> 18:24.520
if you don't like it,

18:24.520 --> 18:25.650
you can get a refund.

18:25.720 --> 18:26.160
Right?

18:26.800 --> 18:28.130
Do you know what he said?

18:29.320 --> 18:31.240
He told me to compensate him ten times the amount.

18:31.240 --> 18:32.040
Why should I?

18:32.560 --> 18:34.200
That's not the most annoying part.

18:34.200 --> 18:35.460
The most annoying part

18:35.520 --> 18:37.360
is that he said our conversation

18:37.880 --> 18:39.610
He recorded the whole process.

18:39.720 --> 18:40.640
That's fine.

18:41.200 --> 18:43.400
Then please prepare all your recordings.

18:43.400 --> 18:44.720
We'll see you in court.

18:46.840 --> 18:48.600
Sir, what are you talking about?

18:48.600 --> 18:50.640
We are talking about secret recording.

18:50.640 --> 18:51.370
I'm so angry.

18:51.680 --> 18:53.680
Do you know what this behavior is called?

18:53.680 --> 18:54.680
This is called...

18:54.680 --> 18:56.240
Invasion of privacy.

18:57.400 --> 18:59.080
I have video recording in this room.

18:59.080 --> 19:00.280
I'm not afraid of him.

19:00.680 --> 19:01.320
Xiaocen.

19:02.440 --> 19:03.700
What do you want to say?

19:06.960 --> 19:07.560
I'm sorry.

19:09.920 --> 19:10.980
I'm sorry, Xu Xiao.

19:13.560 --> 19:15.220
I shouldn't have recorded it.

19:20.080 --> 19:21.720
Mr. Fatty, you want to go for a walk, right?

19:21.720 --> 19:23.380
I was wondering what I forgot.

19:28.960 --> 19:30.490
What are you talking about?

19:31.680 --> 19:33.320
Weren't you guys just talking about

19:33.320 --> 19:34.680
my recording?

19:35.240 --> 19:35.800
No.

19:42.880 --> 19:43.960
I... Then I'll go to work.

19:43.960 --> 19:44.480
Wait.

19:49.240 --> 19:50.240
Whose recording?

19:51.240 --> 19:54.280
Just the sound of you working.

19:54.640 --> 19:55.640
When I'm working?

19:56.520 --> 19:59.120
The sound of you cleaning and polishing.

20:00.600 --> 20:02.200
You mean white noise, right?

20:02.360 --> 20:02.800
Yes.

20:03.480 --> 20:05.540
There's a lot of that on the internet.

20:05.880 --> 20:07.880
I've had insomnia these past two days.

20:07.880 --> 20:09.400
I tried many methods.

20:10.040 --> 20:11.840
But yours is the most effective.

20:14.240 --> 20:15.080
I'm sorry, Xu Xiao.

20:15.080 --> 20:16.440
I won't do it again.

20:16.600 --> 20:17.200
It's fine.

20:20.600 --> 20:21.130
Let's go.

20:21.720 --> 20:22.380
Get to work.

20:35.800 --> 20:37.530
Whose voice are you recording?

20:37.800 --> 20:40.840
Just your voice when you are working.

20:41.880 --> 20:43.920
I've had insomnia these past two days.

20:43.920 --> 20:45.360
I've tried many methods.

20:46.120 --> 20:47.920
But yours is the most effective.

21:01.720 --> 21:03.240
I'm downstairs at your place.

21:03.240 --> 21:04.500
Come down for a moment.

21:09.320 --> 21:11.320
Mom, I'm going downstairs for a bit.

21:12.040 --> 21:13.170
Where are you going?

21:13.440 --> 21:16.080
I'm going downstairs to buy something to drink.

21:16.080 --> 21:16.680
Oh, right.

21:17.200 --> 21:19.160
Buy a couple bags of chips for Xiaoxing.

21:19.160 --> 21:19.960
He loves them.

21:20.920 --> 21:21.600
Got it.

21:29.920 --> 21:30.600
Xu Xiao.

21:32.080 --> 21:33.480
Why did you ask me to come?

21:34.960 --> 21:35.820
This is for you.

21:39.560 --> 21:40.560
I'll be going now.

21:41.840 --> 21:42.570
What is this?

21:43.360 --> 21:44.090
It's for you.

21:45.120 --> 21:46.580
Why are you giving me this?

21:48.800 --> 21:50.000
Anyway, it's for you.

21:52.880 --> 21:54.280
Open it when you get back.

21:55.560 --> 21:56.890
Y-You put it away first.

21:59.800 --> 22:00.730
I'm leaving now.

22:02.440 --> 22:02.920
Okay.

22:03.240 --> 22:03.680
Bye.

22:03.760 --> 22:04.200
Bye.

22:45.840 --> 22:46.640
Here's the thing.

22:46.640 --> 22:49.840
I've been having insomnia a lot lately.

22:50.360 --> 22:51.760
I've tried many methods,

22:52.640 --> 22:54.080
but yours works best.
